    "At each iteration, the loss L(θ) from Equation ( 4) is computed via forward projection, while the gradients ∂L/∂r and ∂L/∂t are computed through automatic differentiation.",
    "We adopt the Adam optimizer with learning rate η = 10 -3 to update the pose parameters.",
    "To prevent numerical instability, we constrain r ∈ [-2π, 2π] and t within physically reasonable bounds (as specified in Section 3.1).",
